Ruby/Informix installation
----------------------------

1. Building Requirements
	* Informix CSDK 2.90

2. Building instructions

   Unix

$ ruby extconf.rb --with-informix-include=$INFORMIXDIR/incl/esql \
     --with-informix-lib=$INFORMIXDIR/lib:$INFORMIXDIR/lib/esql
$ make
# make install


   Windows

$ ruby extconf.rb --with-informix-include=%INFORMIXDIR%\incl\esql --with-informix-lib=%INFORMIXDIR%\lib
$ nmake
$ nmake install
